Paul Young and Gary Numan (1980s) By: Max Date: 14 Mar 2011 Rating: Track 3, Come Back - Has some really cool rifts of the late Paul Young's track "Come Back and Stay". Track 10, Hiding all the Stars - Has some really cool rifts of Gary Numan's "Here in My Car". Both are 80's classics! The whole CD is put together really well. I haven't heard a track I don't like. The tracks I mentioned above are by far my favorites on the CD however, Track 11, "What Am I Doing Here? Pt. 2" also brings out Chicane's unique sound. I really have enjoyed the CD. Quite the surprise for a house genre. Enjoy - Max
